{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-qinfeng-010__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-qinfeng-010", "source_id": "guofeng-qinfeng-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·秦風·010.1", "text_original": "於我乎，夏屋渠渠，今也每食無餘。于嗟乎！不承權輿。", "text_normalized": "於我乎，夏屋渠渠，今也每食無餘。于嗟乎！不承權輿。", "notes": "權輿 Chinese stanza 1."}
